Photo, Community Canvas: Spray-can artists use the rear wall of the Levitz 
Furniture warehouse on the Los Angeles River in Atwater as their own 
ever-changing canvas. Most days find several artists toiling side by side on 
their own projects, covering up artwork from the previous day. RICK MEYER / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
