MOSES; ORIENTAL RUG CENTER (STORE); UNDERWRITING; CORPORATIONS; SPONSORS; 
TELEVISION ADVERTISING; PUBLIC BROADCASTING SERVICE; KCET (TELEVISION STATION); 
GOVERNMENT REFORM 
</P>
